<tr>
<td style="text-align:right;" colspan="2">
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;; font-size:xx-small;">This box: <a href="/wiki/Template:Infobox_Botanical_product" title="Template:Infobox Botanical product"><span title="View this template" style="">view</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Infobox_Botanical_product" title="Template talk:Infobox Botanical product"><span title="Discussion about this template" style="">talk</span></a></div>
