<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Opium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History</span></h2>
<p><a name="Ancient_use_.284200_BC_-_800_AD.29" id="Ancient_use_.284200_BC_-_800_AD.29"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Opium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Ancient use (4200 BC - 800 AD)">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Ancient use (4200 BC - 800 AD)</span></h3>
